{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"720","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"俄羅斯西伯利亞飆高溫 北極圈小鎮38度破紀錄","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/06/22&nbsp; 09:04</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8C%97%E6%A5%B5%E5%9C%88.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 600px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>俄羅斯薩哈共和國的維爾霍揚斯克鎮在北極圈內，位於首都莫斯科東北方大約<span lang='EN-US'>4660</span>公里處。圖為維爾霍揚斯克鎮入口處紀念碑。（圖取自維基共享資源，版權屬公有領域）</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社莫斯科<span lang='EN-US'>21</span>日綜合外電報導）根據氣象數據網站的資料顯示，過去曾出現攝氏零下<span lang='EN-US'>68</span>度極端低溫的俄羅斯西伯利亞小鎮維爾霍揚斯克（<span lang='EN-US'>Verkhoyansk</span>），竟在昨天測得攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>38</span>度高溫。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>美聯社報導，彙整俄羅斯氣象數據網站<span lang='EN-US'>Pogoda i Klimat</span>的資料指出，維爾霍揚斯克鎮<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>日高溫達到攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>38</span>度（華氏<span lang='EN-US'>100.4</span>度）。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>俄羅斯薩哈共和國（<span lang='EN-US'>Sakha Republic</span>）的維爾霍揚斯克鎮在北極圈內，位於首都莫斯科（<span lang='EN-US'>Moscow</span>）東北方大約<span lang='EN-US'>4660</span>公里處。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E7%B6%AD%E7%88%BE%E9%9C%8D%E6%8F%9A%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 649px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>過去曾出現攝氏零下<span lang='EN-US'>68</span>度極端低溫的俄羅斯西伯利亞小鎮維爾霍揚斯克（紅標處），在<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>日測得攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>38</span>度高溫。（圖取自<span lang='EN-US'>Google</span>地圖網頁<span lang='EN-US'>google.com/maps</span>）</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>維爾霍揚斯克鎮約有<span lang='EN-US'>1300</span>位居民，金氏世界紀錄（<span lang='EN-US'>Guinness World Records</span>）認證這座城鎮出現過最極端的溫差，當地曾測到攝氏零下<span lang='EN-US'>68</span>度極端低溫，過去的高溫紀錄則為攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>37.2</span>度。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>西伯利亞大部分地區今年出現異常高溫，導致大規模野火重創當地森林。（譯者：陳彥鈞）<span lang='EN-US'>1090622</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006220004.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-06-22","clk_count":"274"}},"__N_SSG":true}